Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:33.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiations have broken down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:35.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey! I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've forgotten me already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:11.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:24.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Hughes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:29.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Agent Hughes from the NIA, and \NI report directly to the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the person in charge \Nof this series of missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:36.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you listen to what I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why you're apprehensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to run away, you \Ncould wait until after we talk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real sucker for coffee, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still? You still haven't found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The army is getting special reinforcements \Nand searching the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Special forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the big boys here, what \Ndo they think they're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghost is one thing, but why is it \Ntaking so long to find one little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are continuing to use thermal \Nsensors to perform our own search.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:36.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we will find them \Neventually if we stay calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:43.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem here is that we adults \Nare being made fools of by a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:44.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show that brat who he's dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as good as Hilly's, but it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known, we could have \Nworked something out earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:24.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, what a surprise to \Nlearn you knew the Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman's name isn't Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you call it Heroman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the relationship between you \Nand that robot... I mean, Heroman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:48.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:54.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I received command of this \Noperation two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a shot of Heroman from a \Nsecurity camera at one of the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:04.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to find out its identity, \NI came to Center City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to confirm or deny the \Nexistence of hyper-advanced technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as secure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The government is scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of your power, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone destroyed the Skrugg,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:27.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who the entire might of the United \NStates military wasn't able to scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And their identity is still a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:31.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was thinking of doing something \Nlike this from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to talk with the Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody that wanted to conquer the world \Nisn't going to help the city rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, all the people at the construction \Nsites said the same thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:53.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That you guys are allies of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone said that about Heroman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:57.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm convinced now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A person who can smile like you can't be evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the altitude lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't ask the impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:35.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what'll happen if \Nwe drop any lower, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanna get picked up on the military's \Nradar and taken to the woodshed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm, it'll be fine. My info is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the power of the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:55.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how much they try and keep \Npeople silent, the info always leaks out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A government plot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And behind it all is Dr. Minami with his deep \Nconnections to higher-ups in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know who's behind it, so if we can bring \Nit to light, this'll be a big scandal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:11.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to pile on \Nthe pressure to broadcast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly why we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not paid enough for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:39.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Point 302, no sign of the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Point 257, no sign of the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:54.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So it really was you \Nwho defeated the Skrugg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:58.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We were just trying to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:04.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we've been trying to get \Nrid of the saviors of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think it came to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had been able to speak with you \Nfirst, this would never have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:19.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a reaction from the thermal sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not seem to be the Ghost. We \Nhave confirmed a boy and Agent Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:37.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be taken for observation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:50.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and be subject to intense government \Nexperiments for the rest of your life in captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power that destroyed the Skrugg \Nis definitely something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:02.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But turning the tables
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:09.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and using force to oppress someone with \Npower greater than ours isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:15.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First we need to decide on a way we can \Ncooperate instead of being enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a promise. I report directly to the \NPresident of the United States, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll let you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's end all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that we can talk at leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Block his communications, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all forces! The target \Nhas been spotted at point 451!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This NIA agent is cooperating with the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a traitor to the United States, \Nand is colluding with the Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:42.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate him together with the Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:48.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is with regret that I now assume \Ncommand of this operation from the NIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you all to deeply impress me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:56.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle will determine \Nthe fate of the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must completely destroy the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: You must destroy the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can tell, I've been set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, let's get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning attack toward target!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Set up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil man who has wheedled \Nhis way into the government
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is trying to crush our peaceful negotiations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the doings of a man who knows \Nhow to deal with the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:33.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about your promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm dead, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can get word through the appropriate \Nchannels, we can counter his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:52.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's why he's trying to silence me \Nbefore I get a chance to get the word out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:03.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, I can't die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, would you like to help me with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry and show yourself, Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Target confirmed. It is the Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:46.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can stop them here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to split up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:35.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find a way to send a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:39.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, I need you to keep their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:14:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can stop them here, then \Nwe won't have to run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect, perfect! This is \Nall going according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amanorich and Stallion are \Nat the scheduled location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems we're also right where we should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:21.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we let the Ghost's combat ability \Nbe made clear during the military's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then after they've had quite \Nenough of the Ghost's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I take the Ghost and crush it with my robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Start up the electromagnetic pulse cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stallion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Our attacks are completely ineffective!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we have any stronger weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:29.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is art in movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:38.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Dr. Minami, have invented the strongest,\Nultimate weapon in the entire universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin Ghost! You minion of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:53.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure you taste \Nthe wrath of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,E!! M!! P!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:27.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to pay that high tuition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I took data during our last battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible defensive ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And even more incredible battle strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:52.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be overstating it to say that you \Ncould defeat any weapon on this planet easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a crucial weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:05.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not equipped with \Nany long range weaponry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:16.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I stay outside of your attack \Nrange, there's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have any information?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:41.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Feeling glum, Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:46.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is going to be settled at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to find some way \Nto get close to that robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to do that, I have \Nto do something about that weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:21.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This fearsome weapon is a indeed an \Nelectromagnetic pulse generator!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Electromagnetic pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Dr. Minami, will lecture you uneducated fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:34.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This electromagnetic pulse generator
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,was developed from a system that spreads out \Nelectromagnetic waves over a large area,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:44.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,into a weapon that uses semiconductors \Nand electricity for complete destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Electromagnetic waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:50.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is hyper-advanced technology, \Nthe Ghost is still a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:53.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One hit with this and it'll be all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just set up the relay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an exclusive! A total scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:07.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningless unless we do it live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break! No edits, no way, no how!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, none of the other media have noticed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the scoop of the century!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really mind either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you noticed then say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and connect the relay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.79,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Keisha, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've figured out we can't \Nfire in quick succession?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapid charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:38.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. Doing that would cause \Nthe machine to become immobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:11.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all forces! Halt hostilities at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:20.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order from the President \Nof the United States of America!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:23.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat: End the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:31.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:36.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Minami, surrender at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:38.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:45.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it. Just like you asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this battle now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:53.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... At this rate, \NHeroman's energy will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With his true intentions revealed, Dr. \NMinami continues his attack on Heroman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a standoff with Dr. Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:11.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, light is shined on the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:15.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #16: Decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:18.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
